fields.description: A representative from Goldman  Sachs is coming into DUCSS to talk about internship and careers opportunities with Goldman Sachs in Dublin and London. This is the first of many events that will be held throughout the year aimed at connecting members with tech companies in Ireland and aboard. At this event there is also free pizza and light refreshments.
